Usable with 1½ wide roll or 2 individual 3/4 inch wide rolls, by simply turning the large knob the model 5000 applies the tape to a star wheel for easy removal. Perfect for gift wrap, retail, and industrial applications where a 1½ inch piece of tape is required, the Model #5000 also has a separate free mandrel for 3/4 inch tape with unlimited lengths.
